uk.ac.ebi.utils.collections

Class MapCollection<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.utils.collections.MapCollection<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<V>, Collection<V>

    public class MapCollection<K,V>
extends Object
implements Collection<V>

    Creates a view of a Map that is a collection. Does so by using a keyFunc function, which applies to map values.

    WARNING: Not fully tested yet!

    Author:
    brandizi
    Date:
    15 Oct 2015
